Yes, mostly in California.

**What kind of car do you drive? Or what is your dream car?**

I drive a toyota pickup truck, and a jeep wrangler 4x4. Both have 5 speed manual transmissions.

My former car (which was at one point a dream car) was a red '88 jeep cherokee pioneer, to the best of my knowledge it is still working and being driven around the reno nevada area. Another dream car is one with a rotary engine, having bought and sold a mazda rx8 I can write that one off the list. (why not?)